&lt;li&gt;Understanding of and a good network into the CUAS system integrator ecosystem&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Organized and detail-oriented with excellent follow-up skills&amp;nbsp;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Demonstrated technical acumen and the ability to articulate technical concepts&amp;nbsp;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Ability to develop a partner plan that aligns with the overall corporate strategic plan&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/li&gt;
