&lt;li&gt;Experience leading a multi-disciplinary engineering team developing hybrid products and systems comprised of broad spectrum of hardware and software components, such as:&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Electrical Printed Circuit Board Assemblies, including digital, analog, mixed signal, and RF circuits&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Mechanical components and assemblies with structural, shielding, and thermal management functions&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Custom, semicustom, programmable, and off-the-shelf digital and mixed signal integrated circuits&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Embedded firmware, embedded operating system, and application-level software&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Middleware and companion applications that interface with hardware platforms&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Demonstrated leadership in system architecture definition and decomposition, including definition of systems and subsystems requirements&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Experience with Design for Excellence methodologies and Continuous Improvement to achieve designs that are producible, reliable, durable, and perform as expected&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Excellent communication and collaboration

